textAfterTable: 10 Songs Biography Formed: 2007 in Arkansas Genre: Christian & Gospel Years Active: '00s, '10s Charles Moore had been a member of the Georgia Mass Choir for some 14 years, and when he relocated from Georgia to Bentonville, Arkansas, he began looking for a similar choir to join. Not finding such a choir, Moore started making inquiries about forming one for the state of Arkansas, and by the spring of 2007 he had assembled the 132-voice Arkansas Gospel Mass Choir.
